cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.CV

This paper proposes a method for safe and efficient reinforcement learning in practical settings such as robotics, which involves learning a forward and reset policy simultaneously. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses the use of value function for the reset policy, which suggests a connection to cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the experiments involve visual inputs, indicating a possible connection to cs.CV (Computer Vision).
